# nanobot core

Files under `nanobot/` are the **core engine** maintained by the external community.

- **Minimize edits** to reduce merge conflicts when pulling upstream.
- If you must change something here, **document what and why** in `docs/reference/` (e.g. architecture.md or a short overrides note) so the next merge is easier to resolve.
